VI'm very hard of hearing (according to my wife), and have to have the TV sound up to 20-22 while she prefers 15-16. I have found myself cupping my hand over my "good" ear, just to make out dialog in my favorite shows. I did a lot of research and wound up ordering these wireless headphones. WOW, what a difference. They were simple to set up (had to find the correct output on my TV), but what a difference. I watched a recorded program (Homeland) and was even able to hear birds and crickets in the background, as well as all of the dialog, clearly. What an incredible difference! The velour earpieces are extremely confortable and can be worn all evening. I highly recommend these to anyone struggling to hear their favorite shows.
