VLove my wireless headphone set!
p1945
sg5
VThese are wonderful headphones. This is my first set of wireless headphones and I love the freedom they provide. I am still getting used to not getting snagged on a cord. It's incredible getting up and going to the kitchen or the bathroom and being able to hear everything. My purpose for buying headphones is to be able to watch movies silently so as not to disturb my neighbors. These are great. The sound is very good. I find that when I watch one of my favorite TV series (The Good Wife) that they seem to do something with the background noise that somehow creates the illusion of sound coming from other parts of my room. I don't know how to explain it but I will try. For example, when I watch a scene from this show and there people chatting (in addition to whoever the camera is focusing on) in the background I almost feel as though I hear people talking in my apartment in the next room. Oddly, I don't seem to experience this with any other show or movie I have watched so far. It's truly an incredible audio effect and I feel as though I'm hearing sound from speakers somewhere in the room and not from the actual headphones themselves. The headphones fit quite comfortably on my large head but the sound truly is good. It doesn't seem to have a lot of bass for listening to dance music but it serves my purpose well; watching television and movie disks.I've had these for about three months. The instructions in PDF format that comes on a CD-ROM disk are a lot more thorough than the small booklet that comes with the headphones. I bought the receiver with headset and also an additional headset so that a guest and I can watch television and not disturb my neighbors. Pairing is a breeze and I am very pleased with my purchase. I would buy these again.
