VWhat a GIANT waste of money
p3519
sg5
VWhat a GIANT waste of money !!!I'm an owner of RS 120 and RS 220 and now I've decided to get RS 180 for my house.  After receiving them I was stunned as how cheaply these headphones are made. Plastic band which goes over the head is flimsier than $20 headphones you can buy at Target. Plastic components of the head band are not screwed or glued together, they are just holding to each other with small plastic notches which immediately snapped as i as putting headphones on.Comparing to RS 130 and RS 220, for some reason ear caps do not go completely over the ear, they are little smaller which makes these headphones on ear. Sound has decent bass but dull compared to RS 220, definitely is missing thigh and mid frequencies.I'll be returning this junk shortly, originally these headphones are $300+ but I got them on sale for $199, well to tell you the truth, they don't worth than $50 to me. I would rather spend extra 100$ and get another pair of RS 220 than use these headphones. It's a shame how Sennheiser could produce such a lame product
